{"tid":255063,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人愈大愈主動遠離愛情","createTime":"2017-05-23T15:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T13:25:09.000Z","uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"171d7fe0092ef4798a8e884b8cbd8ce33b286d77","tid":255063,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T15:42:49.000Z","msg":"唔聽情歌<br />\r\n唔睇愛情片<br />\r\n電視劇角色一談情就返房等過場再出返來睇<br />\r\n街上遇到情侶就耷低頭<br />\r\n異性面前扮傻，撩我傾計就問一句答一句用門面說話敷衍佢等佢冇癮，一係扮阿叔大談人生道理等佢以為我on99，明明講左d野觸動到我笑點都要扮get唔到，仲要一副唔耐煩「下你up乜鳩呀」咁既表情<br />\r\n有次去公司annual dinner合照時間有條女痴埋來企我隔籬，我就扮俾前排遮住行過些少，條女跟住我行，我再行過去兩條男同事中間撇甩佢<br />\r\n有次training兩個人一部機，禁緊mouse個女同事借d意疊隻手落我度，我即刻縮開指住個mon扮教佢<br />\r\n扮忙，扮痴線，扮廢，扮柒，扮唔明，扮聽唔到，仲有咩我係唔識扮"},{"pid":"b351557cc7e37ec3ca02a8498d3ec2f07a7f3370","tid":255063,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/23/234329_ce4bb68d31268ee992db46c9bc264460.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F23%2F234329_ce4bb68d31268ee992db46c9bc264460.jpg&h=39bf154d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7431f404d215ddb011981a5a381c9a844db6b952","tid":255063,"uid":118466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T15:59:09.000Z","msg":"何必呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fbf4599f6348488410c757349163be687fe6e29","tid":255063,"uid":62737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T16:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>何必呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔遠離愛情就真係何必呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n年紀細果陣都仲會對愛情有幻想<br />\n大左就覺得真係可有可無"},{"pid":"4161cac61926ef1f1bc2eb927c97b679223030a0","tid":255063,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T10:55:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>何必呢<img src=\"/assets/face